  "reference_number": "RUS1977",
  "remarks": "\nEvgenii Vasilyevich ISTOMIN is an involved person within the meaning of the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 on the following two grounds:  ISTOMIN is or has been obtaining a benefit from or supporting the Government of Russia from working as a director of an entity (JSC NPP ISTOK) that i) is carrying out business in a sector of strategic significance to the Government of Russia, namely the Russian defence and electronics sectors, and ii) is a Government of Russia – affiliated entity. \n",
